    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This Adversary has the Sharingan, granting it the following benefits;</p><ul><li><p>60 feet of Chakra Sight</p></li><li><p>Can Copy 1 Jutsu it can see cast, without the Hijutsu keyword by spending its Reaction, adding it to its Known list.</p></li><li><p>Add 1d4 bonus to Saving throws made to resist Genjutsu.</p></li><li><p>Genjutsu cast by this Adversary with only the Visual Keyword has its DC increased by +1.</p></li></ul>",
